</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>《安心出行》被發現有人臉辨識功能，資科辦：從未使用並研究刪除</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/05/04/leave-home-safe-android-app-facial-recognition/software/android-app/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=leave-home-safe-android-app-facial-recognition</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[唐美鳳]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 04 May 2022 02:02:53 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[Android App]]></category><category><![CDATA[FactWire]]></category><category><![CDATA[安心出行]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1098373</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>網站 FactWire 日前拆解政府《安心出行》應用程式的 Android 版本時，發現內置人面識別模組，但無法肯定模組在用戶使用程式時有否運作。負責《安心出行》項目的政府資訊科技總監辦公室承認程式內有相關模組，但強調程式毋須使用相關功能，會要求程式開發商研究移除人面識別模組的可行性。</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>網站 FactWire 日前拆解政府《安心出行》應用程式的 Android 版本時，發現內置人面識別模組，但無法肯定模組在用戶使用程式時有否運作。負責《安心出行》項目的政府資訊科技總監辦公室承認程式內有相關模組，但強調程式毋須使用相關功能，會要求程式開發商研究移除人面識別模組的可行性。</p><p><span id="more-1098373"></span></p><p>FactWire 拆解 Android 版《安心出行》程式所發現的人面識別模組，能夠識別五官特徵和位置，相關模組早在 2020 年推出的的《安心出行》早期版本已經存在，但無論是《安心出行》官方網站或手機程式商店的介紹關未有提及。FactWire 指由於政府拒絕公開程式的源代碼，所以無從確認程式運作時是否有進行人面識別。</p><p>在回應傳媒提問時，政府資訊科技總監辦公室承認承辦商在開發《安心出行》程式時，是用來與包含人面識別功能的現成模組，但強調未有使用相關功能。他們已經要求承辦商在不影響程式正常運作下，研究將人面識別模組從程式刪除。</p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.factwire.org/%E5%AE%89%E5%BF%83%E5%87%BA%E8%A1%8C%E5%85%A7%E7%BD%AE%E4%BA%BA%E8%87%89%E8%AD%98%E5%88%A5%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD-%E8%B3%87%E7%A7%91%E8%BE%A6%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D-%E7%A8%B1%E5%BE%9E%E6%9C%AA/">factwire</a></p>
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=BTbnYDWXOAY:1WjezaQ_CCg:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=BTbnYDWXOAY:1WjezaQ_CCg:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Netflix 取消與梅根合作動畫項目，相信與業績倒退有關</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/05/04/netflix-axes-pearl-animated-tv-series-meghan/movie-2/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=netflix-axes-pearl-animated-tv-series-meghan</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[唐美鳳]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 04 May 2022 02:02:52 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[電影 / 劇集]]></category><category><![CDATA[Netflix]]></category><category><![CDATA[Pearl]]></category><category><![CDATA[梅根]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1098372</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>影片串流平臺 Netflix 日前宣佈取消與英國哈里王子的夫人梅根合作的動畫項目，雖然 Netflix 強調是戰略決定，但外界普遍認為因業績倒退，故此要透過取消部份項目以節省資源。早前公佈季度業績時，Netflix 透露上季流失了 20 萬付費帳戶，是十年來首次，Netflix 歸咎競爭激烈和用戶分享帳號所致。</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>影片串流平臺 Netflix 日前宣佈取消與英國哈里王子的夫人梅根合作的動畫項目，雖然 Netflix 強調是戰略決定，但外界普遍認為因業績倒退，故此要透過取消部份項目以節省資源。早前公佈季度業績時，Netflix 透露上季流失了 20 萬付費帳戶，是十年來首次，Netflix 歸咎競爭激烈和用戶分享帳號所致。</p><p><span id="more-1098372"></span></p><p>在兩年前脫離皇室和移居美國後，哈里王子的夫人梅根就成立了製作公司，製作劇集、紀錄片和兒童節目等，其中一個合作夥伴就是 Netflix，他們簽訂了協議共同出版多個項目，包括去年夏季公佈，由梅根參與監製的《Pearl》動畫項目。《Pearl》講述 12 歲女孩受到多名女性歷史人物啟發，尋找自我和克服生活難關的故事。</p><p>《Pearl》除了是哈里王子伉儷製作公司的首齣動畫作品，有指故事的部份靈感來自梅根的童年經歷。雖然 Netflix 宣佈取消《Pearl》項目的合作，但另一齣有關哈里王子為退役殘障軍人舉辦運動會的紀錄片則會繼續。</p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.nbcnews.com/pop-culture/pop-culture-news/netflix-axes-pearl-animated-tv-series-meghan-duchess-sussex-rcna26894">nbcnews</a></p>
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=-q_qdRkkz50:-LF11Yj6pRk:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=-q_qdRkkz50:-LF11Yj6pRk:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>仿效 Apple 環保策略，新 Xperia 旗艦傳不附充電器</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/05/04/xperia-1-iv-no-charger/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=xperia-1-iv-no-charger</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[唐美鳳]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 04 May 2022 02:02:50 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[手提電話]]></category><category><![CDATA[SONY]]></category><category><![CDATA[Xperia 1 IV]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1098371</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>早前 Sony 宣佈將會在 5 月 11 日舉行 Xperia 全球新產品發佈活動，如無意外將會發表旗艦機 Xperia 1 IV。新機除了規格配置的升級，有消息指 Sony 終於將過去三代均採用的 8MP 前置自拍鏡頭，在新機 Xperia 1 IV 升級至 12MP，暫時未知會否同時帶來自拍質素和功能的提升。</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>早前 Sony 宣佈將會在 5 月 11 日舉行 Xperia 全球新產品發佈活動，如無意外將會發表旗艦機 Xperia 1 IV。新機除了規格配置的升級，有消息指 Sony 終於將過去三代均採用的 8MP 前置自拍鏡頭，在新機 Xperia 1 IV 升級至 12MP，暫時未知會否同時帶來自拍質素和功能的提升。</p><p><span id="more-1098371"></span></p><p>另一項改動則比較具爭議性，有指 Sony 將會仿效 Apple、Samsung、小米和華為等廠商，不再為旗艦級 Xperia 1 IV 提供充電器。這項措施相信會受到關注環保的人士歡迎，同時亦會有消費者認為需要額外購買充電器是廠商賺錢的手段。早前中國認證機構出現了一款型號 XQ-CT72 的 Sony 手機，相信是 Xperia 1 IV，資料顯示包裝並不會附有充電器。</p><p>有傳 Xperia 1 IV 的相機會有大更新，主相機將會採用 1/1.3 大尺寸 48MP 感光元件，而超廣角和潛望鏡式變焦鏡頭亦會升級。</p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.notebookcheck.net/Alleged-Sony-Xperia-1-IV-price-leak-suggests-slight-increase-from-Xperia-1-III-but-expected-camera-upgrade-hints-at-substantial-rise.612637.0.html">notebookcheck</a>、onleaks</p>
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=dg5XVBi7F9o:gkpur7blCJg:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=dg5XVBi7F9o:gkpur7blCJg:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>配合各地開關旅遊復甦   Google 推新版旅遊工具</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/05/04/plan-your-summer-travel-with-help-from-google/life-tech/travel/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=plan-your-summer-travel-with-help-from-google</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[唐美鳳]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 04 May 2022 02:02:48 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[旅遊]]></category><category><![CDATA[google]]></category><category><![CDATA[google flights]]></category><category><![CDATA[Google Travel]]></category><category><![CDATA[機票]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1098370</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>全球各地陸續放寬旅客入境措施，意味著人們可以前往外地公幹和旅遊，Google 亦趁機為其旅行籌劃功能作出改動，包括提供長達 6 個月的機票價格追蹤功能。用戶利用 Google Flights 搜尋往來兩地的機票後，可以選擇追蹤票價變化，一旦未來 3 至 6 個月票價下降就會收到電郵提示。</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>全球各地陸續放寬旅客入境措施，意味著人們可以前往外地公幹和旅遊，Google 亦趁機為其旅行籌劃功能作出改動，包括提供長達 6 個月的機票價格追蹤功能。用戶利用 <a href="http://google.com/flights">Google Flights</a> 搜尋往來兩地的機票後，可以選擇追蹤票價變化，一旦未來 3 至 6 個月票價下降就會收到電郵提示。</p><p><span id="more-1098370"></span></p><p>Google Travel 的探索工具 <a href="https://www.google.com/travel/explore">Explore Tool</a> 亦作出更新，用戶可以更容易找到目的地的景點資料，同時會透過地圖指引向用戶提供目的地鄰近觀光景點，前往的交通安排和所需時間等，包括前往的機票最低價格，酒店房價和天氣等。</p><p>不少旅客都希望住處跟旅遊景點或工作的地方盡量靠近，用戶在 Google 搜尋旅遊景點或輸入指定地址，再搜尋附近的酒店和住宿，就會獲得距離該地點 15 至 30 分鐘步程或駕駛距離的住宿選擇，用戶亦可以利用 Bookmark 功能將之儲存，留待日後使用。</p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://blog.google/products/travel/plan-your-summer-travel-with-help-from-google/">Google</a></p>
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=CtQDo4Z6i1o:4HUi5lu9I-4:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=CtQDo4Z6i1o:4HUi5lu9I-4:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>效力 Ford 逾三載工程師，加盟 Apple Car 團隊</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/05/04/longtime-ford-engineer-joins-apple-car-team/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=longtime-ford-engineer-joins-apple-car-team</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[唐美鳳]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 04 May 2022 02:02:46 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[車壇動向]]></category><category><![CDATA[Apple Car]]></category><category><![CDATA[Ford]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1098374</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>《彭博》昨日報導指在安全系統、工程設計和車身內部工程等有豐富經驗的工程師 Desi Ujkashevic，日前已經離開效力超過 30 年的車廠 Ford，並且轉投 Apple 並加入其汽車項目。在轉換工作機構前，Ujkashevic 是 Ford 的汽車安全工程部的全球總監，亦曾經是 Ford 的工程總監。</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>《彭博》昨日報導指在安全系統、工程設計和車身內部工程等有豐富經驗的工程師 Desi Ujkashevic，日前已經離開效力超過 30 年的車廠 Ford，並且轉投 Apple 並加入其汽車項目。在轉換工作機構前，Ujkashevic 是 Ford 的汽車安全工程部的全球總監，亦曾經是 Ford 的工程總監。</p><p><span id="more-1098374"></span></p><p>Ujkashevic 在 1991 年加入 Ford，在過去 30 年曾經參與 Escape、Explorer、Fiesta 和 Focus，還有電動車款的開發工作，她的豐富經驗對 Apple Car 汽車項目，尤其是安全系統相當有用。根據《彭博》之前的報導，Apple 希望 Apple Car 的安全性能夠超越 Tesla 和 Waymo，並且擁有後備系統以防自動駕駛系統失靈。</p><p>為了開發自動駕駛汽車，Apple 不時從 Ford 和其他車廠招攬人手，Apple Car 項目的目標近年多次改變，領導問題持續出現，不過最新傳聞指 Apple 有望在 2030 年前將汽車產品推出。</p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2022/05/03/longtime-ford-engineer-joins-apple-car-team/">macrumors</a></p>
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=kGF9wyMVBmI:OGYHMmyKPNI:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=kGF9wyMVBmI:OGYHMmyKPNI:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>【評測】SteelSeries Aerox 5 / Aerox 5     多孔設計 + 超長氣 180 小時</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/05/03/aerox-5-aerox-5-wireless-aerox-9-wireless/wireless-home/desktop-pc/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=aerox-5-aerox-5-wireless-aerox-9-wireless</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Harold]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 03 May 2022 12:23:04 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[桌上電腦]]></category><category><![CDATA[Aerox 5]]></category><category><![CDATA[Aerox 5 Wireless]]></category><category><![CDATA[Aerox 9 Wireless]]></category><category><![CDATA[SteelSeries]]></category><category><![CDATA[電競滑鼠]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1098004</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>不少電競玩家開始追求更好的遊戲體驗，機身輕盈方便操作的輕量級電競滑鼠似乎主導了消費市場。SteelSeries [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>不少電競玩家開始追求更好的遊戲體驗，機身輕盈方便操作的輕量級電競滑鼠似乎主導了消費市場。SteelSeries 就推出了 3 款電競滑鼠，分別是 Aerox 5、Aerox 5 Wireless 和 Aerox 9 Wireless。3 款滑鼠各有千秋，將輕巧的性能與滑鼠左側的附加按鈕相結合，增加了實用性。事不宜遲，讓小編馬上實測一下。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0017.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098364" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0017-694x580.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0017-694x580.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0017-768x641.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0017.jpg 861w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1098006 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07819-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07819-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07819-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07819-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07819-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07819-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07819-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Aerox 5 Aerox 5 Wireless Aerox 9 Wireless</p><h2>輕巧多孔設計，防塵防水</h2><p>Aerox 5、Aerox 5 Wireless 和 Aerox 9 Wireless 採用全尺寸設計，長 125 毫米，握把寬 63 毫米，高 42 毫米，小編認送符合人體工程學的外殼形狀能舒適地握在玩家的手中。三者均採用蜂窩狀外殼，這有助減輕滑鼠重量。RGB 可以通過外殼發出明亮的光芒，讓玩家在使用時有視覺的享受。為了幫助保護這種多孔設計，這三款滑鼠還具有 IP54 等級，玩家毋需擔心灰塵和飛濺的水。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1098008 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07815-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07815-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07815-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07815-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07815-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07815-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07815-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Aerox 5 蜂窩狀外殼</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1098009 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07799-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07799-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07799-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07799-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07799-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07799-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07799-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Aerox 5 Wireless 蜂窩狀外殼</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1098007 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07786-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07786-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07786-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07786-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07786-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07786-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07786-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ Aerox 9 Wireless RGB 可以通過外殼發出明亮的光芒</p><h2>Quantum 2.0 無線技術，可使用 180 小時</h2><p>Aerox 5 Wireless 和 Aerox 9 Wireless 用上了 Quantum 2.0 無線技術和藍牙連接，NextGen Golden Micro IP54 按鍵經計算可達 8,000 萬次點擊，較其他電競滑鼠耐用度高出 3 倍。電量方面，玩家可使用長達 180 小時，電量耗盡後，只需充電 15 分鐘即可享逾 40 個小時。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1098011 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07809-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07809-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07809-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07809-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07809-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07809-2048x1366.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07809-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Aerox 5 Wireless 用上了 Quantum 2.0 無線技術和藍牙連接</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1098010 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07797-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07797-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07797-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07797-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07797-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07797-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07797-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ Aerox 9 Wireless 用上了 Quantum 2.0 無線技術和藍牙連接</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1098013 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07805-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07805-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07805-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07805-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07805-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07805-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07805-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Quantum 2.0 無線技術和藍牙連接</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1098012 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07800-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07800-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07800-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07800-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07800-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07800-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07800-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲NextGen Golden Micro IP54 按鍵經計算可達 8,000 萬次點擊</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1098014 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07806-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07806-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07806-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07806-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07806-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07806-2048x1366.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07806-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲電量耗盡後，只需充電 15 分鐘即可用逾 40 個小時</p><h2>輕量設計，實際重量比官方數字重 1 至 2 克</h2><p>Aerox 5 和 Aerox 5 Wireless 相差無幾，只是在於有線與無線之別。Aerox 5 Wireless 的無線設計，可讓玩家無限制和束縛，盡情擺動滑鼠。Aerox 5 和 Aerox 5 Wireless 都時以輕量見稱，Aerox 5 淨重 66 克，而 Aerox 5 Wireless 則重 74 克。小編認為其實不大影響，對比兩者不太實際地感受到。小編將兩者放上磅，前者淨重 67 克，後者是 76 克，與官方指出的重量只差 1 至 2 克。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1098016 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07822-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07822-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07822-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07822-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07822-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07822-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07822-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Aerox 5 重 67 克</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0005.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098358" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0005-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0005-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0005-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0005.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲Aerox 5 握感良好</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1098017 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07823-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07823-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07823-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07823-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07823-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07823-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07823-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ Aerox 5 Wireless 重 76 克</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0008.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098359" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0008-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0008-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0008-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0008.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"> ▲Aerox 5 Wireless 無線連接之餘重量更只有 76 克，使用時感覺極輕身</p><h2>「Aerox 5、Aerox 5 Wireless」9 鍵設計</h2><p>Aerox 5 和 Aerox 5 Wireless 均以 9 鍵設計，分別是食指和中指控制的左右鍵、中間的滾輪及按鍵，還有用姆指控制的 4 個快捷鍵。小編認為，部份按鍵比較難按下。如中間的 DPI 按鍵，設計在滑鼠接近中間的位置，使用食指和中指均較難接觸到。另外，在姆指部份，小編覺得銀色按鍵可以設計得再靠後一些，現時只可僅僅按得下，可能女士或手短偏短的玩家就要留意。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1098022 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07815-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07815-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07815-1-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07815-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07815-1-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07815-1-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07815-1-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1098020 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07801-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07801-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07801-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07801-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07801-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07801-2048x1366.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07801-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲DPI 按鍵使用食指和中指均較難接觸</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1098018 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07814-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07814-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07814-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07814-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07814-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07814-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07814-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1098019 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07803-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07803-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07803-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07803-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07803-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07803-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07803-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲銀色按鍵可以設計得再靠後一些，現時只可僅僅按得下</p><h2>「Aerox 9 Wireless」12 個數字鍵，密集細小</h2><p>Aerox 9 Wireless 外形與 Aerox 5 和 Aerox 5 Wireless 幾乎一樣，唯一分別是左側列出了 12 個數字鍵，可任由玩家自定義，大大增加可塑性。但小編認為，利用姆指控制 12 個數字鍵，有一定的難度。皆因按鍵密集細小，要花一定時間練習如何細緻地控制。而 10、11 和 12 號按鍵設計得較後，姆指需要屈曲遷就。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1098024 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07790-694x466.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="466" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07790-694x466.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07790-1280x859.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07790-768x516.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07790-1536x1031.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07790-2048x1375.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07790-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Aerox 9 Wireless</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1098023 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07791-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07791-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07791-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07791-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07791-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07791-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07791-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲左側列出了 12 個數字鍵，可任由玩家自定義</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1098025 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07791-2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07791-2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07791-2-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07791-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07791-2-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07791-2-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07791-2-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲10、11 和 12 號按鍵設計得較後，姆指需要屈曲遷就</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0004.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098360" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0004-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0004-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0004-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0004.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Aerox 9 Wireless 多了 3  排按鍵方便就手執行玩家預先設定的指令</p><p>雖然 Aerox 9 Wireless 亦以輕量設計，但比 Aerox 5 和 Aerox 5 Wireless 重，官方重量為 89 克。小編將其放上磅，同為 89 克，並沒有偏差。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1098026 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07824-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07824-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07824-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07824-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07824-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07824-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07824-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Aerox 9 Wireless 重 89 克</p><h2>TrueMove Air 感應器 PTFE 滑鼠腳墊，提高精準度</h2><p>Aerox 5、 Aerox 5 Wireless 和 Aerox 9 Wireless 使用了 TrueMove Air 感應器以 100% 原生級 PTFE 滑鼠腳墊，能協助玩家提高精準度。身為電競滑鼠，一定要實測一下遊戲表現。小編分別用 Aerox 5、 Aerox 5 Wireless 和 Aerox 9 Wireless 遊玩 Back 4 Blood。受惠於 TrueMove Air 感應器和 100% 原生級 PTFE 滑鼠腳墊，可以輕鬆描準目標，提升玩家滿足感。在遊玩期間，重量或許是分勝負的關鍵，較輕的 Aerox 5 和 Aerox 5 Wireless 操控較為得心應手，來去自如。但相對重的 Aerox 9 Wireless 則有少許輸蝕，明顯感覺到 Aerox 9 Wireless 沒有前兩者靈活。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1098028 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07789-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07789-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07789-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07789-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07789-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07789-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/KAN07789-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲TrueMove Air 感應器和 100% 原生級 PTFE 滑鼠腳墊</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1098029 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Back-4-Blood-Screenshot-2022.04.29-15.51.27.56-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Back-4-Blood-Screenshot-2022.04.29-15.51.27.56-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Back-4-Blood-Screenshot-2022.04.29-15.51.27.56-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Back-4-Blood-Screenshot-2022.04.29-15.51.27.56-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Back-4-Blood-Screenshot-2022.04.29-15.51.27.56-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Back-4-Blood-Screenshot-2022.04.29-15.51.27.56-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Back-4-Blood-Screenshot-2022.04.29-15.51.27.56-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Back 4 Blood</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1098031 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Back-4-Blood-Screenshot-2022.04.29-16.11.15.99-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Back-4-Blood-Screenshot-2022.04.29-16.11.15.99-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Back-4-Blood-Screenshot-2022.04.29-16.11.15.99-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Back-4-Blood-Screenshot-2022.04.29-16.11.15.99-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Back-4-Blood-Screenshot-2022.04.29-16.11.15.99-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Back-4-Blood-Screenshot-2022.04.29-16.11.15.99-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Back-4-Blood-Screenshot-2022.04.29-16.11.15.99-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">▲輕鬆描準目標</span></p><h2>總結</h2><p>整體而言，這三款電競滑鼠兼備了舒適和實用，輕巧的機身使操控力提高，更能準確地對準目標，絕對適合打機及日常使用。Aerox 5 價錢相對便宜，適合新手入門。Aerox 5 Wireless 適合有預算的玩家，無論是新手或老手皆宜。Aerox 9 Wireless 則適合要求高玩家，可自定義更多，當然價錢亦會相應較高。</p></p><div class="feedflare">
